&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with software engineers, data engineers, and product stakeholders to integrate ML solutions into CompanyCam&#39;s platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate clearly with non-technical audiences about feasibility, requirements, and trade-offs of proposed solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
